cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.RO 

The paper discusses the use of artificial agents for vision-based reinforcement learning tasks, which falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and robotics (cs.RO). The use of neuroevolution for training these agents also suggests the category of neural networks (cs.NE).
